{
  "stem": "9730.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so he was an all-around man for that job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it-- it was on one of the major streets in-- in that town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a two-story house, as-- as so many others were there, in the back of which we had a garden, in which we grew a lot of the things, vegetables and so on, and flowers.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that helped be almost-- well, not quite self-sufficient, but it helped in general, because this was also considered the country, because it was a small town, so we had access to-- to a lot of produce that we might not have had in a city.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's name was Ludwig, L-U-D-W-I-G, Klein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had six other brothers and three sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was born and grew up in the same house I was born in and grew up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took over my grandfather's business, which had to do with-- with hops and tobacco and-- and grain, which was being auctioned off among the farmers in that area.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they were brokers for those, for produce and for those products, and would sell 'em.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For instance, the hops, my father would process the hops and treat them, and-- and-- and sell them to the breweries.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he-- he was actually something of a scholarly type.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he he didn't show emotions too easily, but he was a very caring person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, in fact, I-- I-- I never remember having any harsh words with him or from his side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it-- I had a lot of respect for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was more or less forced to take over this business, at a time when perhaps he should have become or gone-- become an academic or something like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
